      • trySetPaginationStrategy

        public boolean trySetPaginationStrategy(int paginationStrategy)
        Try to modify the pagination strategy. The modification of pagination strategy is allowed only once during initialization. Sample code that can be used in a WizardExtensionBehavior :- public void initPage(String pageBeingShown) { if(getPaginationData() != null){ getPaginationData().trySetPaginationStrategy(YRCPaginationData.YRC_GENERIC_PAGINATION_STRATEGY); } }
